Package: macos-auth
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: libc6, libpam0g
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Maintainer: macos-auth contributors <noreply@example.invalid>
Homepage: https://github.com/rioriost/macos-auth
Description: Linux PAM helper for macOS-backed authentication approval
 macos-auth is an experimental PAM module and Linux helper for approving
 Linux authentication requests through a macOS user-session agent.
 .
 This package installs the Linux helper, PAM module, documentation, and
 example PAM snippets. It does not modify /etc/pam.d/sudo automatically.
